Two weeks, an overwhelming 1000+ applications for #theworldsbestjob!
The next few days are going to be long but exciting, as we narrow down on our Top 100.
Our six mentors will announce their 5 picks first, PowerDrift adds another 20 candidates to the list, and our team at Harley-Davidson rounds it up with our favourite 50. 
The shortlisted 100 will make it through to the next round.
Keep an eye on our stories, and hold on to your helmet.

latestPosts.caption:
The H-D X440 pack is ready to roll towards Umling La - and the energy is electric!

The ride begins today. Wish them luck as they prep for this incredible adventure.

#HarleyDavidson #HarleyDavidsonIndia #HDIndia #HDI #DestinationX #HDX440 #UmlingLa

The Destination X ride to Umling La kicks off tomorrow and it’s going to be one epic journey!

Some of our H-D X440 riders have started their route from Delhi to Manali, where they’ll meet the rest of the crew before the big ride begins.

Stay tuned to our page for daily updates.

#HarleyDavidson #HarleyDavidsonIndia #HDIndia #HDI #DestinationX #HDX440 #UmlingLa

In just two days, our H-D X440 riders begin their epic ride to Umling La - the world’s highest motorable pass!

Riders from Chandigarh are already on the move, heading to the starting point in Manali.

Stay tuned as they prepare to take on stunning landscapes and create memories that’ll last a lifetime!
